{"tid":2366380,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我阿哥係咸濕定妹控。。。","createTime":"2021-01-14T12:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T13:09:43.000Z","uid":35348,"like":32,"dislike":971,"uniUserReply":100,"replies":[{"pid":"32baa2367f4e1eb2f1857f64fce9cfedb1c21f90","tid":2366380,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"小妹11歲，細粒，人稱女神、校花 等 ；<br />\n有個16歲阿哥，ok la 唔醜樣，鍾意睇**打**<br />\n<br />\n我阿哥成日......<br />\n<br />\n- 食我口水尾（我食唔晒嗰啲早餐下午茶）<br />\n- 問我啲好尷尬嘅問題（唔駛我多講.....）<br />\n- 係我面前扯住旗換褲（<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n- 趁機抓住我隻手唔放（佢隻手好多手汗)<br />\n- 望住我條裙嘅下半部，有次望到流鼻血 <br />\n- 主動幫我著襪，趁機睇裙底（我唔鍾意著打底褲但只鍾意著裙）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多......<br />\n<br />\n最嚴重係，<br />\n我習慣晏晝就沖涼，父母好晏先返，每次我沖到一半，佢都會入嚟「洗手」，但佢唔會望住佢隻手而係望住我。（我屋企浴缸門係用防霧破璃，冇裝窗簾）<br />\n<br />\n我寫緊嗰陣，唸唸下，其實只要佢唔再過份啲，蝕小小比佢都冇乜所謂啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5506e550a55b655ce82891e07d0c2631f338e648","tid":2366380,"uid":61281,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa98897b7491e6a259439a4260d0be855552670e","tid":2366380,"uid":211486,"like":398,"dislike":2,"score":396,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"假膠 拉"},{"pid":"5b20d5ba5f0296417eedfbdb92c9d9b607c498c1","tid":2366380,"uid":180466,"like":545,"dislike":2,"score":543,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:12.000Z","msg":"連登真係好多痴線佬"},{"pid":"86eb40a4119fe4049f6ffd589ecf7587ac0f0920","tid":2366380,"uid":201182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:21.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"c44fe2721e0c7ce2bba9e3cd7290e7f93917a3df","tid":2366380,"uid":293783,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:28.000Z","msg":"阿哥上緊連登"},{"pid":"bd699d1dab52427838bb85d0c8d32aa397d931c9","tid":2366380,"uid":38189,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"樓主留電話 我signal同你傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b55e6dcff4aa522adb16f6f505d904fcaea166b","tid":2366380,"uid":35348,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"5506e550a55b655ce82891e07d0c2631f338e648","tid":2366380,"uid":61281,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"笑乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e180c08039bafac820c3bc6ade9650fadd82ffed","tid":2366380,"uid":363330,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"係個咸濕嘅妹控<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a586160e06ab8dfa8c22cdf152e084ed193eb8","tid":2366380,"uid":331194,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"Why not both，做呀妹就直接屌鳩佢，一係同老豆老母講。<br />\nBtw流鼻血單野應該就唔關事"},{"pid":"7ea657142639a39dcc0f899fc296c6363f7f8e56","tid":2366380,"uid":35348,"like":6,"dislike":34,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"bd699d1dab52427838bb85d0c8d32aa397d931c9","tid":2366380,"uid":38189,"like":25,"dislike":7,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:31:34.000Z","msg":"樓主留電話 我signal同你傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:32:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac