 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n- 趁機抓住我隻手唔放（佢隻手好多手汗)<br />\n- 望住我條裙嘅下半部，有次望到流鼻血 <br />\n- 主動幫我著襪，趁機睇裙底（我唔鍾意著打底褲但只鍾意著裙）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多......<br />\n<br />\n最嚴重係，<br />\n我習慣晏晝就沖涼，父母好晏先返，每次我沖到一半，佢都會入嚟「洗手」，但佢唔會望住佢隻手而係望住我。（我屋企浴缸門係用防霧破璃，冇裝窗簾）<br />\n<br />\n我寫緊嗰陣，唸唸下，其實只要佢唔再過份啲，蝕小小比佢都冇乜所謂啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T12:59:26.000Z","msg":"挑唔贏CC台就轉陣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過開下依d post咪幾好 野野玩火犯眾憎啦"},{"pid":"1fdd94db820de1ce667a463e50f05a7e7faed57c","tid":2366380,"uid":10592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"3e4b029989ff2970e11e4efd9d8c99cd6da9f8a2","tid":2366380,"uid":33189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:04:53.000Z","msg":"FF少陣巴打"},{"pid":"c1940ae4df297821ed3ae42f7912c4769db8cdf4","tid":2366380,"uid":6980,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"夢遺巴一排冇入post<br />\n原來痴咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edcd161412b95a03ba8fc4596cf3dcd55523855","tid":2366380,"uid":385190,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HD5j0Rv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHD5j0Rv.jpg&h=3af35a55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bd7bc8bf71b56f63e2d12e092ed74f96928173f","tid":2366380,"uid":39206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T13:05:51.000Z","msg":"po你個樣來睇下幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"h